description: Try our easy to follow Tacos with Southern Style Crumbed Fish Bites & Mexican Bean Salad recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Tacos with Southern Style Crumbed Fish Bites & Mexican Bean Salad
name: Tacos with Southern Style Crumbed Fish Bites & Mexican Bean Salad Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g southern style crumbed fish bites

recipeInstructions.text: Cook Southern Style Crumbed Fish Bites and chunky chips according to the packet instructions. Serve fish bites divided in Mexican taco shells with bean salad, sour cream, lime wedges and chips.
